                        <interp inst="t18360704-name-221" type="surname" value="BURNS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360704-name-221" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM BURNS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am apprentice on board <hi rend="italic">The Johns Renwick</hi> in the West India Dicks. On Sunday evening, the 3rd of July I saw the two prisoner—Brown had a bundle under his arm—he went beside some deals—I went to peep. and saw Wiffin putting on a pair of blue trowsers, and he put his own on over them—as soon as they saw us peeping they put the bundle under the deals.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Wiffin</hi>. I found the trowsers, and I took them down behind the deals, but I did not put them on.</p>
